A. faster document finishing
B. increased use of color
C. increased number of first-time resolution of printer issues

investment (ROI)?
A. by overriding toner low messages
B. by encouraging the use of digital sending
C. by increasing device utilization rates
D. by redirecting print jobs to available devices
